author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drywall cutting tip for exhaust fan…I mark the location of the fan with my speed square. Then I set the tip on my RotoZip to 3/4” and use the fan body as my guide. This is extremely helpful and reduces errors. By the way, Ziggy is an awesome helper 🐶🔥#drywall #exhaustfan #bathroomremodel #homerepairtutor
title: Drywall Cutting Tip for Exhaust Fan - #shorts #homerepairtutor
